name: Work Overtime
description:
Made for Game Off 2022

Quickly deliver the items to their stops in the store but don't use up too much time at the vending machine becuase time is money.

Controls

  • Space: To interact with vending machine, item, or store shelf
  • Escape: Close vending machine

I started this half way through November lol and had to go away for thanksgiving so I didn't spend a lot of time on it.
